content:
I think there's been another misunderstanding! As a conversational AI, I don't have personal experiences or memories, so I don't recall any interactions with Sarah or any previous conversations about her. Each time you interact with me, it's a new conversation and I don't retain any information.

But I'd be happy to help you with book recommendations! What genre or type of books are you in the mood for? Fiction, non-fiction, mystery, sci-fi, fantasy, or something else? Let me know, and I can suggest some titles or authors that might interest you!
